---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="AI Implementation & Automation | Sentinel Nexus"
  description="From opportunity identification to production deployment, we implement intelligent automation that drives efficiency, reduces costs, and creates competitive advantage."
>
  <section class="hero-service">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pillar-badge">Pillar 1</div>
      <h1>AI Implementation & Automation</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Build AI That Actually Works</p>
      <p class="hero-description">
        From opportunity identification to production deployment, we implement intelligent automation that drives efficiency, reduces costs, and creates competitive advantage.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-block">
        <h2>Transform Operations with Intelligent Automation</h2>
        <p>
          Most AI initiatives fail not because the technology isn't ready, but because implementation lacks rigor. We bring a structured approach to AI deployment—grounded in real-world operational experience—that ensures your automation investments deliver measurable results.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're automating document processing, deploying conversational AI, or building custom ML solutions, we handle the complexity so you can focus on outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What We Deliver</h2>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>AI Readiness Assessments</h3>
          <p>Evaluate your organization's AI maturity and identify the highest-impact opportunities for automation. We assess data infrastructure, process complexity, and organizational readiness to build a prioritized roadmap.</p>
          <a href="/ai-implementation/ai-readiness-assessments" class="learn-more">What is an AI Readiness Assessment? &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Workflow Automation & Process Redesign</h3>
          <p>Transform manual, repetitive processes into intelligent workflows. We analyze existing operations, identify automation candidates, and implement solutions that integrate seamlessly with your tech stack.</p>
           <a href="/ai-implementation/workflow-automation-process-redesign" class="learn-more">What is Workflow Automation & Process Redesign? &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Custom AI/ML Solution Development</h3>
          <p>Build bespoke machine learning models tailored to your specific business challenges. From predictive analytics to natural language processing, we develop solutions that deliver competitive advantage.</p>
          <a href="/ai-implementation/custom-ai-ml-solution-development" class="learn-more">What is Custom AI/ML Solution Development? &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Agentic AI Orchestration</h3>
          <p>Deploy autonomous AI agents that can reason, plan, and execute complex multi-step tasks. Our agentic systems go beyond simple automation to handle dynamic workflows requiring judgment and adaptation.</p>
          <a href="/ai-implementation/agentic-ai-orchestration" class="learn-more">What is Agentic AI Orchestration? &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>System Integration</h3>
          <p>Connect AI capabilities to your existing enterprise systems—ERP, CRM, ITSM, and beyond. We ensure seamless data flow and process orchestration across your technology ecosystem.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Intelligent Document Processing</h3>
          <p>Extract, classify, and process unstructured data from documents at scale. Transform invoices, contracts, forms, and correspondence into structured, actionable information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Conversational AI Deployment</h3>
          <p>Implement AI-powered chatbots and virtual assistants that understand context and deliver value. From customer service to internal support, we build conversational experiences that work.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Hyperautomation Strategy</h3>
          <p>Orchestrate multiple automation technologies—RPA, AI/ML, process mining—into a cohesive hyperautomation program. Maximize the compound value of your automation investments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">We follow a rigorous ML lifecycle methodology that ensures every AI initiative is grounded in your business reality.</p>

      <div class="approach-grid">
        <div class="approach-card">
          <div class="approach-number">01</div>
          <h3>Domain Understanding</h3>
          <p>We start by deeply understanding your business context, goals, and the specific challenges AI can address.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-card">
          <div class="approach-number">02</div>
          <h3>Data Discovery</h3>
          <p>Identify and unify data sources across modalities—accounting for dependencies and context that inform accurate modeling.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-card">
          <div class="approach-number">03</div>
          <h3>Data Preparation</h3>
          <p>Combine automated analysis with manual review to filter noise, validate quality, and structure data into model-ready formats.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-card">
          <div class="approach-number">04</div>
          <h3>Feature Engineering</h3>
          <p>Apply domain expertise to extract meaningful signals from raw data—the differentiator between models that work and models that excel.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-card">
          <div class="approach-number">05</div>
          <h3>Model Development</h3>
          <p>Build, test, and rigorously evaluate models against real-world performance criteria, not just accuracy metrics.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-card">
          <div class="approach-number">06</div>
          <h3>Deployment & Monitoring</h3>
          <p>Deploy production-ready solutions with ongoing monitoring to ensure sustained performance and quick adaptation to drift.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Expected Outcomes</h2>

      <div class="outcomes-grid">
        <div class="outcome-card">
          <div class="outcome-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"></polyline><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Faster Operations</h3>
          <p>Reduce process cycle times by 40-80% through intelligent automation of manual workflows.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="outcome-card">
          <div class="outcome-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Reduced Costs</h3>
          <p>Lower operational costs through automation while redirecting human effort to higher-value work.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="outcome-card">
          <div class="outcome-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Competitive Edge</h3>
          <p>Deploy AI capabilities that differentiate your organization and create sustainable competitive advantage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to implement AI that actually works?</h2>
      <p>Let's discuss how intelligent automation can transform your operations.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" data-umami-event="{AI Implementation | Start a Conversation Btn}">Start a Conversation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-service {
    padding: 10rem 0 4rem;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, var(--color-bg) 70%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pillar-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-service h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-dark {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .intro-block {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro-block h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro-block p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .learn-more {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .learn-more:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .approach-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .approach-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .approach-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .approach-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .outcomes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .outcome-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .outcome-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .outcome-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .outcome-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .section-cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-1) 0%, #1e40af 100%);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-cta p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .section-cta .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
  }

  .section-cta .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f0f0f0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-service {
      padding: 8rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .services-grid,
    .approach-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
